boat.com/blog.images/natural-compounds-boost-bone-implant-success-while-killing-bacteria-and-cancer-cells.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 23:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/natural-compounds-boost-bone-implant-success-while-killing-bacteria-and-cancer-cells</guid></item><item><title>肿瘤学中的噬菌体疗法：癌症预防和治疗的机会</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/phage-therapy-in-oncology-opportunities-for-cancer-prevention-and-treatment</link><description>噬菌体疗法在癌症预防和治疗中的应用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/phage-therapy-in-oncology-opportunities-for-cancer-prevention-and-treatment2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 12:36:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/phage-therapy-in-oncology-opportunities-for-cancer-prevention-and-treatment</guid></item><item><title>质量从哪里来？科学家发现新奇核状态的证据</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/where-does-mass-come-from-scientists-find-evidence-of-a-new-exotic-nuclear-state</link><description>新的实验揭示了可能的 η′-mesic 核，提供了粒子质量在核物质内部移动的证据，并揭示了质量如何起源于真空结构。我们周围的几乎所有事物都具有质量，但其起源仍然是物理学中的一个基本问题。目前的理论建议&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/where-does-mass-come-from-scientists-find-evidence-of-a-new-exotic-nuclear-state.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 12:21:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/where-does-mass-come-from-scientists-find-evidence-of-a-new-exotic-nuclear-state</guid></item><item><title>革命性的成像技术以极快的速度解开物质的秘密</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/revolutionary-imaging-technique-unlocks-secrets-of-matter-at-extreme-speeds</link><description>一种新颖的成像方法通过结合激光编码和人工智能重建，以前所未有的细节捕捉超快事件。研究人员引入了一种新的成像方法，与早期的方法相比，该方法可以揭示微观世界中超快事件的更多细节。该技术允许&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/revolutionary-imaging-technique-unlocks-secrets-of-matter-at-extreme-speeds.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>S